thread.title_full: BRIEF-DocCheck unit buys 10 pct of newly established Fysio24 | Reuters

author: Reuters
title: BRIEF-DocCheck unit buys 10 pct of newly established Fysio24
text:
Sept 30 DocCheck Ag :
* DocCheck Guano AG, a 100 percent subsidiary of DocCheck AG, buys 10 percent of the newly established Dutch company Fysio24 B.V. with a cash contribution
* Parties agreed not to disclose purchase price Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (Gdynia Newsroom)
